Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}花有荣枯之期
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:03:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}水有无尽之流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}纪灵引军来犯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小沛危在旦夕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你 你竟然能在这里其乐融融啊你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有何不乐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他来犯小沛又不是犯我徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我愁什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我跟你说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小沛一旦失守
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们徐州城等于失去屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唇亡齿寒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你又收了袁术的粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}答应不助刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这两难的处境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想过如何应对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你刚才有听到貂蝉的曲辞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她唱得可妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她唱得是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天无绝人之路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}地有好生之德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}花有荣枯之期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}水有无尽之流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说她这词好不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张飞就是因为贪杯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才丢失了徐州城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你难道要学他的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去重蹈覆辙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个匹夫 怎么能跟我相提并论呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有赤兔马 有方天画戟 那好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也送你两句唱辞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军情如火 生死万急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你赶快给我率军出城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好好 我去就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱妾 等我回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀主公 吕布刚刚发兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 何时能来小沛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布率军至五里坡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在那摆了一席酒宴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说是要请主公前去赴宴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}赴宴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大战迫在眉睫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生死决于一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他怎么能有闲情逸致喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也不解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此宴能退敌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:05:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布这厮早就被袁术给收买了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他设下这鸿门宴是想取大哥的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哥哥万万不能上当啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 吕布收了袁术二十万粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们不得不防啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这就去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我相信吕布不会害我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为了抵御袁术大军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就算身陷险地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也该亲身一试
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哥哥如若真去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那由我来护驾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你和吕布一见面就会打起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万万不可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}俺非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}子龙 云长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们坚守城池
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去去就来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥千万小心哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟 你看吕布军威严整
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此人不仅是个酒色之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是个能征善战的勇将啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贼吕布 贼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二位将军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家主公有令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请两位入营相叙请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德 你日后得志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可别忘了在下今日之恩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上将军之恩 在下并不敢忘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}纪灵将军到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别别别 翼德兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}千万别动兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不是你兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}随你随你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是就不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是不是琼浆美酒的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}俺张飞那是千杯不醉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}言过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备出征那天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不就大醉了一场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天我高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特请两位朋友来陪我喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来呀 干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如此美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如有乐曲相伴就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可惜啊貂蝉不在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她如在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:08:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}酒不醉人人自醉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敢问上将军 你要杀我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不杀 不杀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么你要杀这大耳贼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}找死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不杀 都不杀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然都不杀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就请将军撤去酒席
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让我和纪将军来决战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可 断断不可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我吕布虽然杀人无数
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我平生不好斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最好解斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日我请二位来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是想杯酒释兵戈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上将军你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敢问阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可以开多少斤弓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可射多少步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将不才
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可开他五百斤硬弓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.93,0:09:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}五十步内 箭头穿胸而过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请问张翼德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可以开多少斤弓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可射多少步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}俺可以开八百斤弓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}八十步内 箭头穿甲而过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好 来人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}取我方天画戟 插于辕门之下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}列位随我来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此去辕门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不少一百二十步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果我一箭射中戟上小枝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们则罢兵言和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果射不中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们只管厮杀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是战是和 俱凭天意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们看是如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天下无人能射这么远
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更何况射中戟上的小枝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可能 万万不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是战是和净凭天意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但愿天助吕布 此箭中的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贼吕布 吹牛皮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军请
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}宝雕弓何在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好 好 好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个贼吕布 好生了得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是上天令你们罢兵言和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁敢违背天意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我吕布只有替天行道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再射一支金翎箭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将他穿胸而过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下退兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那吕布辕门射戟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迫使我们双方罢兵休战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他说 谁敢抗拒天意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:13:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他 他就替天行道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个三姓家奴太过可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先前骗走我二十万军饷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在又自做轻薄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}搞什么辕门儿戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}坏我大事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是可忍孰不可忍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}众将听令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令你们速速整军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要亲征吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再取刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}且慢 且慢 且慢 且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请主公息怒 请主公息怒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下以为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果主公派兵赶杀吕布的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对主公有诸多不利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}首先是我们送他的二十万粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可就真的助贼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其二这样就把吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又赶到了刘备那边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们联起手来防御我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个结果正是曹操所愿哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成大事者不能拘小利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可吕布这厮太可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请主公不要只是恨自己的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样会妨碍你的判断力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公可记得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操对他的死敌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那经常是亲密无比
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}笑脸相迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个奸雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他比吕布更可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下以为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布固然可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是辕门射戟一事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}足见其勇冠天下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公想建树大业
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就要忍常人所不忍之事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公树吕布为强敌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何不可以把吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}变为我们的强援呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公啊 来日方长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报 禀主公 怀义校尉孙策觐见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 小霸王孙策来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快召进来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将孙策 拜见主公
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孙策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说说这些年来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我待你如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公待我如君如父 恩重如山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我令你三十天之内夺取庐江城
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么不遵行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在已经是第十三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你竟然还没有出兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀主公
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:16:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将已经攻陷了庐江城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无稽之谈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}庐江距此八百多里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一来一往最少也要二十天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更何况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}庐江太守陆康拥军上万
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}据城坚守
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你孙策就是再善战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有三十天的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你根本拿不下那个重镇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是庐江太守陆康的首级
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这 真是陆康
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孙策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你 你真把庐江城拿下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}庐江两郡四县五座城池
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经全部归属主公
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孙策 快说说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是怎么把它攻下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将接到命令后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当天就率领五千轻骑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}星夜兼程奔赴庐江
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三天内纵横八百里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连续攻城拔寨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陆康还没有来得及设防
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就已经被我攻下城池
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好 好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 那我借给你那三万精兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你损失多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公借给我的三万精兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一概没用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只用了他们的战马
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此次战役
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}战马损失四百余匹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}望主公见谅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将交还兵符
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孙郎之勇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起令尊孙坚将军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有过之而无不及啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有孙郎在 何愁吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何惧天下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}苍天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要是有孙郎这样的子嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}死而无憾哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢主公嘉奖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}帅台设宴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要为孙郎庆功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对 对 好 禀主公
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天是家父的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将想去坟前祭奠一番
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊 等你祭父回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.35,0:18:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我再为你庆功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢主公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军留步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.47,0:19:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}黄叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公子 你还是叫我黄盖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}黄将军 找我有事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才在大堂上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁公如此夸你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公子难道没有听出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他的话外之音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么话外之音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁公当众说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如能有孙郎如子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽死无恨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他言下之意是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想收你做他的义子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个我听出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然听出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那公子的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}黄将军的意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁氏宗族 四世三公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天下奇才半出其门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多少人想攀附却苦于无门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术更是拥兵三十余万
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雄居江南数郡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}久怀帝王之志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他早晚会成大业的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公子既然得其厚爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何不借此机会求取进身之道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术他不配做我的义父
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公子一言 英雄本色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先将军孙坚视我如兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无论何时何地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果需要在下效力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下万死无辞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:21:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}黄叔 我记下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲 孩儿看您来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你归天之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}母亲和孩儿迁居曲阿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.17,0:21:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}时受各地诸侯欺凌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}旧日将士星散
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}家产凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孩儿也不得不归从袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孩儿未能继承你的英雄大业
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:22:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孩儿向你请罪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大丈夫生为豪杰死为鬼雄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如不拔剑而起建功立业
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岂不愧对先父天灵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.37,0:22:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孙策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.98,0:22:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我从庐江城就开始追你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}足足追了八百多里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.58,0:22:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天总算是追上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早知道你要来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.99,0:22:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就让你再追我八百里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.47,0:23:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}家父病亡之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.48,0:23:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我母亲悲伤过度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.78,0:23:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也跟随父亲而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已是无牵无挂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}飘然一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.76,0:23:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你打算以后怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.77,0:23:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我把所有祖产跟田地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.37,0:23:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}全部换成了钱粮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.87,0:23:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}得钱五万
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.97,0:23:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前来投奔你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.68,0:23:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我愿跟你一同实现昔日的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}纵横天下 共创大业
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.89,0:24:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}周瑜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.19,0:24:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.59,0:24:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天是我十年来最高兴的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.67,0:24:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.37,0:24:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术并非英主
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.07,0:24:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如欲成就大业
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.37,0:24:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}首先你必须要脱离袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.38,0:24:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这一点我早就想过了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.38,0:24:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只是担心他会舍不得放我走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.29,0:24:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那方传国玉玺还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.19,0:24:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}送给他 换回自由之身
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.36,0:24:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说的倒是潇洒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.37,0:24:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.27,0:24:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我父亲就是因为它
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.67,0:24:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丢掉了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.07,0:24:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且多少诸侯 袅雄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.47,0:24:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都对它梦寐以求
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.18,0:25:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不就是一块石头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.18,0:25:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大丈夫手提三尺剑即可纵横天下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.98,0:25:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何吝区区俗物
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.69,0:25:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孙权也曾经说过你这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.89,0:25:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他也说这玉玺是祸水
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.70,0:25:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}留之有害而无益
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.47,0:25:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然有见识
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.27,0:25:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这孙权到哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.67,0:25:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么没看见他
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.08,0:25:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他呀 喜欢云游四方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.08,0:25:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在正在各处遍访贤士
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.68,0:25:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说不定过两天就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.99,0:25:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这孙仲谋年少志大
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.09,0:25:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早晚能成一方英豪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.69,0:25:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我母亲在书信里说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.60,0:25:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}扬州刺史刘鹞逼迫日近
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.87,0:26:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要将我全家赶出曲阿
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.27,0:26:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我舅父险些被他谋害
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.28,0:26:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 我想向你借一些兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.98,0:26:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前去曲阿救难省亲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.78,0:26:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请主公恩准
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.59,0:26:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曲阿远在江东
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.69,0:26:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来去路上也得不少日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.30,0:26:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}据报
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.77,0:26:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操和公孙瓒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.47,0:26:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}随时都准备向我用兵
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.97,0:26:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这里大战在即啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.78,0:26:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孙策
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.78,0:26:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我离不开你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.48,0:26:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不这么的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.39,0:26:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我派人到曲阿
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.29,0:26:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把你母亲接到南阳来住
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.49,0:26:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我保证她富贵终身
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.49,0:27:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 曲阿是故土
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.10,0:27:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}母亲不愿离开
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.47,0:27:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}求主公让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.48,0:27:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也罢 你执意要去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.29,0:27:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就快去快回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.69,0:27:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过 借将士的事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.90,0:27:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有些不便
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.00,0:27:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.40,0:27:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这大战在即啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.47,0:27:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.08,0:27:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是我父亲留下的玉玺
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.28,0:27:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我愿以它为质
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.48,0:27:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玉玺为质 是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.58,0:28:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是传国玉玺
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.99,0:28:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日终得一见哪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.16,0:28:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孙策 你说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.90,0:28:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要多少将士
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.40,0:28:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只要四个人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.70,0:28:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}程普 黄盖 韩当 祖茂
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.31,0:28:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其他人等一概不要
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.48,0:28:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这四个人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.48,0:28:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是令尊孙坚的旧部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.08,0:28:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.98,0:29:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们不只是先父的旧将
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.39,0:29:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们更是我孙策的叔伯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.49,0:29:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}程普 黄盖 韩当 祖茂
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.50,0:29:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.50,0:29:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们愿意随孙策前去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.50,0:29:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将愿随
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.28,0:29:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 那你们就跟他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.89,0:29:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢主公
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.80,0:29:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}四位将军
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.00,0:29:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们有半个时辰回家收拾物品
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.10,0:29:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}带上妻小
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.40,0:29:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在城门外面等你们
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.01,0:29:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公子 真的有这么紧急吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.61,0:30:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对 袁术一旦反悔
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.18,0:30:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就会派军追杀我们
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.18,0:30:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}目前我还不想和他反目成仇
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.78,0:30:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.20,0:30:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恭喜主公
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.50,0:30:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}得此玉玺便是得天意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.31,0:30:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天授玉玺于我主
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.31,0:30:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请我主承天顺命
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.61,0:30:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即位九五 成帝王大业
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.98,0:30:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请我主成帝王大业
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.29,0:30:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看 成大业只怕是孙策
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.99,0:30:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他不但不会回到你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.20,0:30:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}日后
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.90,0:30:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还会成为主公的大敌
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.00,0:30:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生此话什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.40,0:31:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孙策用区区一块石头
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.21,0:31:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就换走了我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.31,0:31:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}黄 程 韩 祖 四员大将
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.91,0:31:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而他们都是其父孙坚
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.18,0:31:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昔日的骁将
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.98,0:31:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孙策的用意
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.99,0:31:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公难道就没有看出他的志向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.19,0:31:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.60,0:31:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}背后有高人指点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.20,0:31:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孙策宁可舍弃玉玺
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.81,0:31:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也要背我而去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.11,0:31:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还能看不出他的志向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.71,0:31:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.01,0:31:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孙策有志向没有实力
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.08,0:31:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就凭他现在区区几千人马
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.59,0:31:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成不了什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.99,0:31:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但愿主公说得是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.99,0:33:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生 你看我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.20,0:33:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人已年过花甲 满面苍桑
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.00,0:33:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}年华将逝 来日无多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.31,0:33:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要再不创立大位
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.71,0:33:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以后就没有时间完成心愿了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.21,0:33:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等我即位后
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.41,0:33:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定拜先生为国师
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.62,0:33:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一人之下 万人之上
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.62,0:33:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.59,0:33:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}青史扬名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.29,0:33:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生 不要再劝了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.49,0:33:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 请主公见谅
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.40,0:33:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下生性固执
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.50,0:33:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}宁可直言死于谏
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.60,0:33:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不愿谄媚图荣华
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.70,0:33:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.31,0:33:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你万万不可做皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.71,0:33:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何不可
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.01,0:33:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当年高皇帝刘邦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.71,0:34:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}官位不过泗上一亭长
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.52,0:34:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手中不过三尺剑
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.92,0:34:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}随从不过数十人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.19,0:34:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就敢谋取天下
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.89,0:34:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在汉廷已延年四百年
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.49,0:34:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}气数已尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.60,0:34:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当今四海沸腾
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.60,0:34:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袅雄纷起
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.00,0:34:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}强者为王
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.91,0:34:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}强者之中的强者
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.21,0:34:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就可称帝
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.31,0:34:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我雄居淮南
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.51,0:34:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}粮多地广
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.11,0:34:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拥有精兵四十余万
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.32,0:34:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}强将千余名
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.22,0:34:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁能与我争锋
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.92,0:34:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁敢与我争雄
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.89,0:34:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公虽是明主贤人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.20,0:34:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可你不是汉高祖刘邦爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.20,0:34:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当今世上就有两人可与主公相争
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.41,0:34:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁 谁 谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.61,0:35:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}邺郡袁绍 许昌曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.51,0:35:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍曾任十八镇诸侯盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.32,0:35:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他现在占领着冀 青 并三州
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.82,0:35:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且图谋攻打北方的幽州
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.82,0:35:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他现在拥兵有五十万
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.06,0:35:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}帐下文臣武将皆是海内的豪杰
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.80,0:35:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且还是主公的堂兄
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.70,0:35:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}名望比主公高
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.50,0:35:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操更为当世奸雄
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.61,0:35:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其文才武略 百年罕见
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.91,0:35:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然眼下势力不及主公
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.21,0:35:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是他挟天子令诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.02,0:35:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}执天下牛耳
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.12,0:35:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}远交近攻 纵横南北
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.82,0:35:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其兵威已经是日盛一日
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.99,0:35:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有此二人在
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.00,0:35:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公啊 你做不得皇帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.70,0:36:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍本是我们袁家小妾生的一庶子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.01,0:36:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要论族上卑贱
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.61,0:36:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他只配给我当奴仆
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.51,0:36:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就是看他比我年长两岁
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.12,0:36:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}认他为兄而已
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.02,0:36:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他敢跟我较量
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.62,0:36:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有那个曹阿瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.22,0:36:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他原本就是奸宦之后
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.73,0:36:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贱民之孙
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.63,0:36:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}鹰犬之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.73,0:36:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无耻之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.40,0:36:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到时候
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.20,0:36:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我继了王位
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.30,0:36:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一个出兵灭掉的就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.40,0:36:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要杀鸡儆猴 彰显天威
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.52,0:36:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣等拜见主公
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.62,0:36:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.12,0:36:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣等三百五十五名文武官员
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.53,0:37:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}联名向主公上表
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.33,0:37:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请主公顺天承命 即皇帝位
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.10,0:37:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}改元开国
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.80,0:37:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.01,0:37:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这 这 这么大的事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.91,0:37:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要三思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.51,0:37:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 若你不能顺天承命
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.52,0:37:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老臣今日就叩死在你面前
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.72,0:37:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请主公顺天即位 改元开国
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.23,0:37:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好 好 众位爱卿
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.10,0:37:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}事已至此
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.50,0:37:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只好上承天命 下顺民心
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.91,0:37:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即皇帝位
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.71,0:37:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公万岁 吾皇万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.83,0:38:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}东汉末年
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.93,0:38:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术率先称帝
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.13,0:38:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}建号仲氏
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.90,0:38:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}立寿春为都
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.00,0:38:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}并布告天下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.01,0:38:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}由此也使各地军阀之间的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.01,0:38:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更加剧烈
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.92,0:38:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术逆天僭位 在寿春开国
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.23,0:38:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还自称是个什么仲氏皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.03,0:38:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他甚至还要让我向他上表称臣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.41,0:38:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么 这无耻的匹夫
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.01,0:38:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胆大包天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.81,0:38:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如论占地之广 拥兵之多
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.51,0:38:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}威望之盛 将士之优良
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.92,0:39:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家主公样样都在袁术之上
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.02,0:39:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要坐皇帝也得我家主公坐
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.32,0:39:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪能轮得着他袁术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.63,0:39:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.53,0:39:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将请主公立刻即皇帝大位
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.13,0:39:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}开国之后
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.43,0:39:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我等必为主公平定天下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.34,0:39:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请主公建国开元
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.21,0:39:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请主公即皇帝大位
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.81,0:39:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 依许攸之见
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.31,0:39:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在天下大乱之际
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.12,0:39:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各路诸侯无非有以下三种选择
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.52,0:39:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其一是扶汉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.22,0:39:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其二是篡汉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.82,0:39:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这其三嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.99,0:39:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是以扶汉为名 行篡汉之实
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.33,0:39:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术急功近利
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.03,0:39:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}采取了公然篡汉自立
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.64,0:39:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是他的愚见
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.21,0:39:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}势必引火烧身
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.61,0:40:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公你一向深谋远虑 高瞻远瞩
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.21,0:40:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此时当取自强之道
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.12,0:40:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}观时待变 后发制人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.12,0:40:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这才是主公你的智慧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.02,0:40:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}列位将军想做开国功勋
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.63,0:40:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}留得青史扬名
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.33,0:40:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这我可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.93,0:40:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过如今
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.93,0:40:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}汉廷犹存 天子仍在
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.63,0:40:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各地诸侯纷纷裂土称霸
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.14,0:40:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天下未定
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.84,0:40:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}远不到主公开国称帝之时
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.11,0:40:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术在桃子未成熟之前
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.31,0:40:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就急于采摘
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.81,0:40:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他只采得满手荆棘
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.01,0:40:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成为众诸侯的公敌
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.22,0:40:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下料定 长者三年 短者数月
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.02,0:40:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术必败
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.82,0:40:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公啊 袁术悍然称帝
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.03,0:40:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公不必为之气恼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.33,0:40:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为这不是恶讯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.63,0:40:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而是主公的喜事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.93,0:41:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 如何是喜事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.14,0:41:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}古往今来 想当皇帝的人多了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.04,0:41:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}凡是想当皇帝的人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.71,0:41:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就越容不得别人当皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.61,0:41:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术悍然称帝
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.12,0:41:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必然招致天下共愤
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.52,0:41:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.42,0:41:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所有的兵锋和愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.32,0:41:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都转移到袁术那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.12,0:41:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公正好趁此攻伐河北
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.13,0:41:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}取幽州各郡
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.63,0:41:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待霸业已成
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.13,0:41:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再回过头来考虑君王帝位之事
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.43,0:41:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总之 让袁术去贪取帝王之名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.64,0:41:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而主公则取帝王之实
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.74,0:41:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到头来有名无实者必自灭
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.71,0:41:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而主公则终将实至名归
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.72,0:41:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}郭图田丰二位大人所言极是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.22,0:41:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但在下以为
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.83,0:42:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 有一件事主公必须先做
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.63,0:42:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那袁术不是让主公上表称臣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.93,0:42:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}依在下之见
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.74,0:42:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公倒不如真就给他上一道奏表
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.34,0:42:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但只是称贺
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.84,0:42:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仅仅只是称贺 而绝非是称臣
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.64,0:42:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日何日 今夕何夕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.02,0:42:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}五月初五
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.82,0:43:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天下的愚夫蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.43,0:43:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}五月初五都爬出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.03,0:43:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道吗 袁术称帝了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.64,0:43:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}差点没把我笑死
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.35,0:43:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看错了袁术 此乃我之过啊
